      "text": "Board Game Top Shop, known in Japan as Tenant Wars (テナントウォーズ, Tenanto Wōzu), is a video board game developed by KID for the PlayStation and Sega Saturn. Although both releases were published in Japan, only the PlayStation version was issued in North America where it was given an \"E\" rating by the ESRB.",
